#8300
Kevin's Watch~


You find yourself on a granite slab-like platform that appears
to hang suspended in the air. An expanse of sky as huge as if
you were perched on a mountaintop covers you. The wierd halo
of the sun gives a disturbing hue to the rolling gray sea of 
clouds two hundred feet below you. The clouds thrash like 
thunderheads concealing the earth from horizon to horizon.


