#8302
Kevin's Watch~


You are still on the mountain lookout known as Kevin's Watch.
As legend suggests, it is here, upon this spire, that Kevin
Landwaster fought his last battle with the evil Lord Foul. The 
air here is thin and does little to ease the tension you feel 
surrounding you. The stone beneath your feet is cold and damp,
but appears to be magically wrought.


