#8303
Kevin's Watch~


The void around you seems fathomless. You hear the emptiness of
the wind. The swift seething of the clouds below you have a 
hypnotic power, sucking at your concentration. Gray gloom thickens
toward midnight at every step of your descent. Long plunges yawn 
all around you.


