#8304
Kevin's Watch~


You are below the cloud level now. Abruptly the sun fades and 
goes out. A pale flash runs through the dank sea of clouds followed
almost at once by thunder. The wind mounts, and rushes wetly at you 
as if it seeks to lift you from this spire. The mountains around 
you disappear into the abyss of clouds above. A bolt of lightning
thrashes past you, illuminating the mad boil and speed of the
clouds. The sky shatters.


