#8305
The Land~


You have entered the Land known so well by Thomas Covenant,
Unbeliever and White Gold Wielder. To the east snakes a dusty 
trail to Mithil Stonedown, and the vastness of the Central
Plains spills out before you to the north. On the northern 
horizon you see the Westron Mountain range, home of the 
giant-wrought Keep of Revelstone. Towering behind you are the 
Southron Mountains and the spire of Kevin's Watch. You see no
way to return.


