#8311
Mithil Stonedown Square~


In the central hub of Mithil Stonedown, the buildings face toward
the center. None of them have more than one story, and all are stone,
but they vary considerably in size and shape--some are round, others
square or rectangular, and still others so irregular from top to 
bottom that they seemed more like squat hollow boulders than buildings.


