#8338
Revelstone Courtyard~


You stand in the courtyard of Revelstone. You are caught by surprise, almost
taking your breath away. Revelstone is a masterwork. It stands in granite
permanence like an enactment of eternity, a timeless achievement formed of
mere lasting rock by some pure, supreme Giantish participation in skill.
Revelstone seems tall enough to provide a foundation for the heavens.


