#8339
Interior of Revelstone~


You marvel at the giantish creation that surrounds you. The walls were
intricately labored--lined and coigned with groups of windows wrought in
prolific and spontaneous multitude of details which appear to be on the
verge of crystallizing into a pattern. The light dances of the polished
walls and overwhelms your senses so that you can not grasp what
patterns might be there.


