#8382
Shattered Hills~


You stand in the Land, some distance from Lord Foul's Creche. The Creche
stands perhaps half a league away across a cracked, bare low-land of dead
soil and rock, a place lain wrecked and riven for so long that it has 
forgotten even the possibility of life. Several hundred yards away from you 
on either side, the ground falls off in sheer cliffs which draw closer to 
each other as they jut outward until they meet at the tip of the promontory
upon which the Creche stands.


