#8399
Demesne of Lord Foul~


The mist here glows with the light of burning stones, but as it swirls,
the red fades into the dank, universal gray of fogs. A wash of heat and
stink of brimstone pour over you. The vile reek melts into a sweeter
smell---attar, the odor of funerals. Fear and bewilderment suck at you
as if you were sinking into a nightmare.


